# File Structure

## Models

- models/user.h
- models/book.h
- models/author.h
- models/borrow.h

These files would contain the database model classes.
They may also include a few methods, such as `save` and `fetch`.

## Database

- database.h

Contains a Database class, which would hold all of the database handling code.

## Windows

- mainwindow.h & mainwindow.cpp

Represent windows.
